  Types, Classes, SysUtils, Graphics, Controls, StdCtrls, ComCtrls, Forms, Menus,
  Dialogs, frxClass, frxDesgn, frxDsgnIntf, frxUtils,
  frxRes, frxDesgnWorkspace, frxCross
